def group_addresses_by_zipcode(addresses_list: str, zipcode: str) -> str:
    streets = []
    nums = []
    addresses = addresses_list.split('')
    for address in addresses:
        address_parts = address.split()
        address_zipcode = ' '.join(address_parts[-2:])
        if address_zipcode == zipcode:
            street_and_town = ' '.join(address_parts[1:-2])
            house_number = address_parts[0]
            streets.append(street_and_town)
            nums.append(house_number)
    if not streets:
        return f'{zipcode}:/'
    return f"{zipcode}:{','.join(streets)}/{','.join(nums)}"
